node.text: Let's do a little bit of night time skin care! I partnered with @glamglow to try out their new #brightmud Dual Action Exfoliating Treatment mask and their #brighteyes eye cream! This mask in particular has been my FAV the last few weeks and I'm positive it'll quickly turn into one of your fav masks as well when you give it a try :) check out the link in my bio for more info and enjoy this video #glambassador

node.text: Sharing my quick night time skin care routine using my @lorealparis Revitalift Derm Intensives Pure Retinol Night Serum. I’ve officially been using this product for a month and it’s now a permanent part of my routine! I love that it’s dermatologist-validated and it delivers the purest form of retinol at an affordable price ❤️ You seriously can’t beat that. Check out my stories for more info! #lorealparispartner

Hi Guys! Doing a full skincare routine with my favorite @skinmedica products! #ad @skinmedica is a luxury skincare brand that’s backed by science, it’s an investment but well worth it in my opinion. I’m loving the results that I’ve seen these past few months. My fave is the AHA/BHA Exfoliating Cleanser which makes my skin as soft as a baby’s 🍑, and I’m also loving the HA5 - it’s a hydrator that leaves my skin silky smooth and 💦. My entire @skinmedica regimen is listed below in the order I use them. You can shop the products here: https://skmnow.co/arnellarmon

Let me know your fav in the comments!

AHA/BHA Exfoliating Cleanser
TNS Essential Serum®

node.text: Dudeeeee I’m so obsessed with the FlawlessBrows & Flawless facial hair remover from @flawlessbeauty. My face is as soft as a baby’s 🍑...no joke. Both devices are so small I can just throw them in my bag for when I’m on the go but still want to look 💯 & save the time I’d usually spend tweezing. They suggest using Flawless Brows in small, circular motions, but I find that using it back and forth works best for me! You can’t even tell that it’s for hair removal, it basically looks like lipstick.  Use code Arnell10 to save 10% off #ad
